      "message": "Should we build this out of the :warnings target in GN?\n\n-Wall isn\u0027t really nearly \"all\".  There\u0027s also \"-Wextra\", and even that doesn\u0027t add everything.\n\nWhat we tend to do with clang is use \"-Weverything\" and then a whole bunch of \"-Wno-this-or-that\" to (really) turn everything on and then spot disable warnings we aren\u0027t clean for yet.\n\nThat\u0027d be a bit of a pain to maintain in two places, but wouldn\u0027t be a big deal if we could have this script slurp in all those flags.",
